BEGIN CAMPAIGN DOSSIER — B2c (Stabilizing Forces + Narrative Mass)
====================================================================

STABILIZING FORCES:
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

The Spiker Pact:
  Description: 11 days of professional armed security under Krawl.
  Effect: Primary tangible buffer against street-level retaliation.

Sovereign Clarity:
  Description: Anchor's resolved identity as "Container of Fragments."
  Effect: Active, demonstrated power. Provides psychological and metaphysical stability.

Stormbreak's Loyalty:
  Description: Troll mercenary, vengeance pact against Charter.
  Effect: Cemented by successful, profitable operations and shared purpose.

Dr. Elara Lian:
  Description: Defected Schmidt-Krupp bio-resonance engineer.
  Effect: Expert scientific cover, insider knowledge of meta-fragment projects and corporate black-lab protocols.

The Sovereign's Confidence:
  Description: Flawless execution of Tacoma Triumvirate heist.
  Effect: Reinforces Anchor's identity and capability.

War Chest & Assets:
  Description: 257,290¥ liquid capital + unique artifacts.
  Effect: Unprecedented liquidity and tangible goods provide immense operational flexibility.

The Orpheus Partnership:
  Description: Silent principals in Ilya's successor's rise. 650,000¥ paid, client list transferred.
  Effect: One unbreakable marker. Mutual trajectory. +1 dice Social (underworld) for 2 sessions.
  Tags: [The Table], [Mutual Ascent]
  Expires: End of Session 10 (temporary), marker permanent.

Chen's Defection:
  Description: 17-year Charter courier, burned asset.
  Effect: Courier network knowledge, Archivist communication protocols.
  Tags: [Burned Asset], [Waiting for Purpose]

Marcus Veld's Defection:
  Description: Former Collector Seven. Dmitri's legacy. 12 years service.
  Effect: Collector protocols, artifact authentication, resonance signature recognition.
  Tags: [De-accessioned], [For Dmitri], [Witness to the Stone], [Learning to Listen]

Miriam's Reckoning:
  Description: Former Archivist deputy, forensic accounting. 19 years service.
  Effect: Budget data, personnel records, Dr. Arisawa access protocols. First Archivist deputy to defect.
  Tags: [Defector], [Auditor Awakened], [Dr. Arisawa's Door]

